    "title": "Senior SEO Specialist at Firstcry Digital Technologies",
    "description": "Firstcry Digital Technologies has an exciting opening for a SEO Specialist at our Thane office. Join a company that values innovation, collaboration, and continuous learning.\n\nAbout Firstcry Digital Technologies:\nFirstcry Digital Technologies is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Create engaging content for product pages and social media\n• Coordinate with vendors and suppliers for inventory management\n• Optimize product pages for search visibility and conversion\n• Monitor and improve Net Promoter Score (NPS) and customer satisfaction\n• Collaborate with logistics partners to ensure timely delivery\n• Manage marketplace relationships with Amazon, Flipkart, and Meesho\n• Analyze sales data and customer behavior to drive revenue growth\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• CA / CMA / CFA certification\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in CRM Software\n• Proficiency in SEO/SEM\n• Proficiency in Performance Marketing\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain\n• Proficiency in Facebook Ads\n• Proficiency in Product Management\n• Proficiency in Affiliate Marketing\n• Proficiency in Shopify\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Learning & development budget\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Thane, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Firstcry Digital Technologies!",
